## ğŸ› Troubleshooting

**Quick Diagnosis:** Run `aii doctor` to check your setup automatically.

| Issue | Solution |
|-------|----------|
| âŒ `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY not found` | Run `aii config init` or `export ANTHROPIC_API_KEY="key"` |
| âŒ `aii command not found` | Restart terminal or check PATH: `uv tool install aiiware-cli` |
| âš ï¸ Slow responses | Check network or try different provider: `aii config init` |
| ğŸ” Need diagnostics | Run `aii doctor` or enable debug: `AII_DEBUG=1 aii your-command` |
| ğŸ”„ LLM timeout errors | Retry logic automatic in v0.4.1, check `aii doctor` for connectivity |
| âš ï¸ Web search not working | Configure Brave Search API key (optional, free DuckDuckGo fallback available) |

